---
title: BBQ-Style Chicken Breast Dinner with Potato Salad and Sugar Snap Peas
description: If you're craving some BBQ but it's too wintery outside to fire up the grill, we've got you covered! This dish delivers the joys of that backyard BBQ sesh, but it all happens in the kitchen in under 30 minutes!
